  dialogNodes:
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'Say, I can see dirt on your hands.


      Have you been gathering
      herbs recently?'
    nextOption: I sure have!
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'Then we can help each other out.


      Sneekalot is not the bravest
      of the Knights, but he''s the only one who can write.


      We need him to
      help us, but he''s too scared.'
    nextOption: Those goblins aren't very friendly...
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'Yes, so please go offer to help him collect the herbs he needs.


      I''m
      sure he will make it worth your time.'
    nextOption: Sure, where is he?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'Just follow the path behind me up the hill into the base before
      you go looking for goblins.


      He should be just inside the gates.'
    nextOption: Ok, I'll go see what he needs
